    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the dark world of «Fast or Dead VR» solo-developed game!<br>Humanity is dying out after a global epidemic. Most of the infected have turned into zombies or mutated. Scattered communities of survivors are preoccupied with two things: survival and plunder. <br>You are a free mercenary, plowing the wasteland in your four-wheeled wreck. Use any opportunity to earn extra money. <br>And remember - any means are good for survival! <br>You'll find an upgrade and customization system, angry zombie pedestrians and surviving car owners, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virtual reality (VR) helmets are supported.</p>",
